    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA318-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa talaimakaḷ tōḻikku “niṉaikkalu niṉai(t)tirō aiya vaṉṟalai maṭap piṭi pulampiya kural eṉpatu collāmō” eṉac colliyatu. ETv, EN, ER, EV: pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa talaimakaṉait tōḻi colliyatu (ET: celavu aḻuṅkiyatu).</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how SHE who was informed about the separation said to the confidantent: “will we not say ‘did you have any thought about the lonely voice of the hard-headed youthful elephant cow?’” ETv, EN, ER, EV: What the confidante said to HIM who was informed about the separation.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA318">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>niṉaikkalu niṉaitirō vaiya vaṉṟunām</l>
<l>paṇaittā ḷōmaip paṭuciṉai payanta</l>
<l>poruntāp pukarniḻa liruntaṉa māka</l>
<l>naṭukkañ ceyyātu naṇṇuvaḻit tōṉṟi</l>
<l rend="indent4">paṭumara mociya voṟṟiya piṉṉar</l>
<l>yoṭittumicai koṇṭa yōṅkumarup piyāṉai</l>
<l>poṟipaṭu taṭakkai curukkip piṟitō</l>
<l>raṟiyiṭai yiṭṭa vaḷavaikku vēṟuṇarn</l>
<l>teṉṟūḻ viṭarakañ cilampap</l>
<l>puṉṟalai maṭappiṭi pulampiya kuralē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you have any though at all, o lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">for the lonely voice of the youthful she-elephant with low head,</l>
<l rend="indent2">so that the sunny(?) inside of the cave resounded,</l>
<l rend="indent">realising differently to the extent that knowing one other thing</l>
<l rend="indent2">intervened(?)<note place="foot">Is this enigmatic phrase meant to convey that she, upon trumpeting, gets an answer from him and thus realises that she is not alone? In that case, the connection with the absolutive curukki is pretty impossible.</note>:</l>
<l rend="indent4">the elephant with high tusks folding</l>
<l rend="indent">[its] broad trunk showing spots, that had taken food, breaking [it] off,</l>
<l rend="indent">{after pressing to breaking point the pliable tree,}</l>
<l rend="indent">appearing on the near(?) way without making [us] tremble,</l>
<l rend="indent2">while we were in the unlinking dappled shade</l>
<l rend="indent">spread by the branches coming from the thick-trunked Ōmai tree,</l>
<l rend="indent4">that day?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
